  <steps>
    <step num="0">Spray the inside of a microwave-safe ceramic mug. Add in flour, cocoa powder, sugar, and baking powder. Mix to combine. </step>
    <step num="1">Add the vegetable oil, milk, and stir until smooth. Stir in the chocolate chips. </step>
    <step num="2">Microwave on high for 1 minute 30 seconds. Let cool completely. </step>
    <step num="3">Top with whipped cream, sprinkle on fresh blueberries, raspberries, and mint. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
